1)
$ sudo git clone git://github.com/ysbaddaden/prax.git /opt/prax
2)
$ cd /opt/prax/
$ ./bin/prax install  

3)
link the apps:

$ cd ~/some_folder/app_name
$ prax link

4)
If you want to start the prax server automatically, add this line to the .profile file:

prax start

5)
http://app_name.dev:3000
